_source.text: After a sad night for Jordyn Wieber on Sunday, when she failed to make into the individual all-around finale, she was back and better than ever today, along with her teammates: Aly Raisman , Gabby Douglas , Kyla Ross and McKayla Maroney .

text: **After** a sad night for Jordyn Wieber on Sunday, when she failed to make into the individual all-around finale, she was back and **better** **than** ever today, along with her teammates: **Aly** **Raisman** , Gabby Douglas , Kyla Ross and **McKayla** **Maroney** .
